-------------------------------------EXO1-------------------------------------

1- 
CLE = UNIX 
PLAINTEXT = MAC/OS 
        a- remove useless char such as the "/"
        b- the key should be in the same length as the plaintext meaning :
        length(UNIX) = length(MACOS) 
        if false then we need to append the first char of the key at the end of the key 
        result UNIXU
        length(UNIXU) = length(MACOS)
        b- using vignere matrix the result will be : 
        CipherText =  GNKLM 
        
2- 
CLE= EBOLA 
CIPHERTEXT= TSCEEKFF
PLAINTEXT = PROTEGER


